      • applyToAllUnaryMethods

        public GroupServiceSettings.Builder applyToAllUnaryMethods(UnaryCallSettings.Builder unaryCallSettings)
                                                    throws Exception
        Applies the given settings to all of the unary API methods in this service. Only values that are non-null will be applied, so this method is not capable of un-setting any values.

        Note: This method does not support applying settings to streaming methods.

        Throws:
        Exception
